name: High Jump Summer Games 2016
description:
Aim high and leap far in the high jump competition in Rio! The bar is set high and you'll have to take a running jump to reach over it without knocking it down to win the gold medal. Beat teams from all over the world to earn your place on the podium.

Time your speed and jump to launch yourself over the bar. But don't knock the bar down or your championship dreams will fall down with it!

- Take part in the high jump!
- Win in the Summer Games!
- Qualify against many rivals!
- Play many stages of the championship!
